page.title: 10Dores/Abriachan_David's Day
page.content: I woke up today and i watched the Television. I went to the toilet and then i got dressed. I ate my breakfast and then I went outside to wait for the Taxi. I arrived at school and Robert,Gavin and I played Football. The bell rang and everyone went inside. Mr.Nicholson our Art Teacher came and we did interesting pictures. We went outside to play and we did High Jump. The bell rang so we went in and started our Maths. We went to Lunch which was quite nice. We went to play outside and we had a game of Football. We had a visit from two ladies who told us about the Dores Gala. We all got a tube of sweets from them.
